name: Yin Yang (ansa, Takinn, sharanyasahu, viviennelin, laurchang)
name_original: Yin Yang (ansa, Takinn, sharanyasahu, viviennelin, laurchang)
description:
Objective: Started out as meeting characters in the middle and keeping them alive, but now it's really just wandering around and picking up objects haha

WASD to move!

Space to jump!

F to switch characters!

E to collect items!

Credits:

Programming: Ansa Schmulbach, Vivienne Lin, Sharanya Sahu

Music: Lauren Chang, Sharanya Sahu

Art: Titilope Akinnitire, Sharanya Sahu, Vivienne Lin
